Contact Us






Curtiss-Wright Products



 The COTS Single Source Provider
Curtiss-Wright Defense Solutions offers the Industry’s broadest and most comprehensive range of standard highly engineered products, providing solutions at every level of COTS system integration. We offer products that range from rugged computer boards and mezzanine modules, to fully integrated, tested, and qualified subsystems, as well as electromechanical systems and naval systems. We lead the Industry in the development of advanced module design, thermal management, and the lifecycle maintenance technologies required to ensure highly reliable system performance in harsh environments.

For specific programmatic requirements that can not be satisfied with standard products, Curtiss-Wright has long been recognized as the embedded aerospace and defense market’s partner of choice for highly demanding custom-built system design and development. We support our customers with unmatched system engineering, programmatic expertise, system packaging, and subsystem development.

With built-in strict adherence to today’s leading open architectures, our rugged COTS board products are available in a wide range of open standard form factors including VPX, OpenVPX, VPX-REDI, VME, and CompactPCI. Mezzanine module types include PMC, XMC and FMC.
 



